fields.bio_summary: Jo-Vaughn Virginie Scott (born January 20, 1995), better known by his stage name Joey Badass (stylized as Joey Bada$$), is an American hip hop recording artist and actor.
fields.name: Joey bada$$

fields.bio_summary: Omnikrom is a Canadian rap, crunk, and electro group formed in Montréal.
fields.name: Omnikrom

fields.bio_summary: Russell Tyrone Jones better known under his stage name Ol' Dirty Bastard (or ODB), was an American rapper and producer. He was one of the founding members of the Wu-Tang Clan.
fields.name: Ol' Dirty Bastard

fields.bio_summary: William Leonard Roberts II (born January 28, 1976), known professionally by his stage name Rick Ross, is an American rapper and entrepreneur.
fields.name: Rick Ross

fields.bio_summary: Dwayne Michael Carter Jr. (born September 27, 1982), known professionally as Lil Wayne, is an American hip hop recording artist and author from New Orleans, Louisiana.
fields.name: Lil Wayne

fields.bio_summary: Quincy Lamont Williams (born August 17, 1984), known by his stage name Peewee Longway is an American hip hop recording artist from Atlanta, Georgia.
fields.name: Peewee Longway
